data.text:
Collection of three items, each signed by a Laotian leader, including: Kaysone Phomvihane (ALS), who was the leader of the Lao People's Revolutionary Party from 1955 until his death in 1992; Khamtai Siphandon (SP), who was president from 1998 to 2006; and Oudone Sananikone (SP signed on the reverse), an aristocrat who served as director general of the military. In overall fine condition, with light contrast to Khamtai Siphandonâ€™s signature. Pre-certified PSA/DNA.
